State of Connecticut v. Matthew J. Wehrle (9610)

Daly, Layeey and Landau, Js.

Argued May 2 decision released May 28, 1991 William Domnarski, for the appellant (defendant). Paul J. Ferencek, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Patricia Swords, state’s attorney, and Sandra Tulius, deputy assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
